2w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/slipknot-venla-shalin-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>本周乐队新面具曝光后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>的粉丝们开始将去年取代键盘手和采样器克雷格·琼斯的神秘成员称为“样本”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353"><b>活结乐队的小丑谈论 2024 年巡演和新材料：“这支乐队从未如此快乐”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>琼斯的离职消息是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-are-seemingly-teasing-a-new-member-3452721">在大约一年前宣布的</a>，他的继任者几乎立即就在九号台在当年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/download-festival">下载节上成为头条新闻之前推出。</a></p><p>令人印象深刻的是，桑普斯先生的身份仍然未知。当他们加入乐队时，粉丝们给他们起了“Greg Bones”、“The Gimp”、“Leatherface”、“Zipper Dude”和“Hoodie Guy”的称号。</p><p>然而，当活结将每个成员的新面具的照片发布到 Instagram 上时，这个新昵称就出现了。样品的名称没有与他们的乐器一起列出，标题只是简单地写着“样品/媒体”，导致人们将它们称为样品或样品媒体。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C66p8z5ROVR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmln